OL,7,FClass Ceiling report co-chair Avis
OL,8,FGilmore who as shocked by the lack of
OL,9,Fpayment for those entering arts
OL,11,FA hard-hitting report showing the lack
OL,12,Fof working-class representation from
OL,13,Fjobs in the arts has suggested a Class
OL,14,FChampion and a more transparent
OL,15,Fapplication process.
OL,17,FA former chief prosecutor and
OL,18,FChancellor of Manchester University
OL,19,Fsays "discrimination against working-
OL,20,Fclass people should be illegal"
