OL,3,CClass bias should be illegal, claims
OL,4,CGreater Manchester 'Class Ceiling'
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FMore than 50% of respondents told the
OL,8,Fmainly Greater Manchester-based Class
OL,9,FCeiling survey they had experienced
OL,10,Fharassment or bias due to their social
OL,11,Fbackground.
OL,13,FIt follows calls for better
OL,14,Fopportunities for working-class
OL,15,Fcreatives, including from award-
OL,16,Fwinning scriptwriter James Graham and
OL,17,Fperformer Jason Manford.
