OL,4,CGreater Manchester 'Class Ceiling'
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FFormer chief prosecutor Nazir Afzal,
OL,8,Fwho is chair of the Lowry arts venue
OL,9,Fin Salford and helped lead the report,
OL,10,Fsaid: "If we want a creative sector
OL,11,Fthat truly reflects modern Britain,
OL,12,Fthen class has to be treated as
OL,13,Fseriously as race, gender and
OL,14,Fdisability."
OL,16,F"This is a national problem, but
OL,17,FGreater Manchester has a chance to
OL,18,Flead the way," he added.
