OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FHe joined calls from the TUC union and
OL,8,Fthe Co-op firm for socioeconomic
OL,9,Fbackground to become the 10th
OL,10,Fprotected characteristic, external
OL,11,Funder the 2010 Equalities Act.
OL,13,FThe inquiry, titled Class Ceiling, was
OL,14,Fco-led by Avis Gilmore, former deputy
OL,15,Fgeneral secretary of the National
OL,16,FEducation Union, alongside Nazir Afzal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
