OL,3,CClass bias should be illegal, claims
OL,4,CGreater Manchester 'Class Ceiling'
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"For decades, working-class people
OL,8,Fhave been told the arts are not for
OL,9,Fthem, and the result is a creative
OL,10,Fsector that has become more elitist,
OL,11,Fnot less," said Avis Gilmore.
OL,13,F"We are wasting an extraordinary
OL,14,Famount of talent because people simply
OL,15,Fcannot afford to get a foot in the
OL,16,Fdoor."
OL,18,F"This report is a blueprint for
OL,19,Fchange, but it needs political will
OL,20,Fand industry commitment," she added.
