OL,3,CClass bias should be illegal, claims
OL,4,CGreater Manchester 'Class Ceiling'
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"If we increase apprenticeships,
OL,8,Fremove unpaid routes into the sector
OL,9,Fand recognise class in equality law,
OL,10,Fwe can finally start to level the
OL,11,Fplaying field for working-class
OL,12,Fcreatives."
OL,14,FThe reports findings reveal that the
OL,15,Farts sector remains dominated by the
OL,16,Fmiddle class, creating what the report
OL,17,Fdescribes as a "class ceiling" that
OL,18,Fblocks the progress of talented people
OL,19,Ffrom working-class backgrounds.
