OL,4,CGreater Manchester 'Class Ceiling'
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FAmong its key proposals, the Class
OL,8,FCeiling report recommends that "class"
OL,9,Fshould be made a protected
OL,10,Fcharacteristic under the Equality Act
OL,11,F2010 ` putting it on the same footing
OL,12,Fas race, sex, and disability.
OL,14,FThe authors argue this change is
OL,15,Fessential to tackling systemic
OL,16,Fbarriers in the creative industries.
OL,26,@pD@`OUpD@fO]
