OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FNazir Afzal said: "In a country where
OL,8,Faround half the population identifies
OL,9,Fas working class, it is simply
OL,10,Funacceptable that so much talent is
OL,11,Flocked out of the arts."
OL,13,F"We've done it before on issues like
OL,14,Fhate crime, and we can do it again by
OL,15,Fsmashing the class ceiling and opening
OL,16,Fdoors for the next generation of
OL,17,Fworking-class artists."
