OL,7,FGreater Manchester Mayor Andy Burnham
OL,8,Fwho was blocked by Labours NEC to
OL,9,Fstand in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,10,Felection gave his backing to the
OL,11,Freport.
OL,13,FDuring his speech, he joked,
OL,14,F'"Fantastic to be here. To be honest,
OL,15,FI've read every single word of this
OL,16,Freport because I haven't had anything
OL,17,Felse to do this weekend."
