OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FHe said he supported the
OL,8,Frecommendations to tackle why
OL,9,Fcreatives from working class
OL,10,Fbackgrounds struggle to break into the
OL,11,Farts.
OL,13,FThe investigation also highlights a
OL,14,Flong-term decline in working-class
OL,15,Frepresentation across artistic fields,
OL,16,Fpointing to deep-rooted structural
OL,17,Fbarriers such as limited access to
OL,18,Fprofessional networks, unpaid
OL,19,Finternships, and high entry costs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
