OL,4,CGreater Manchester 'Class Ceiling'
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FDescribed as a "blueprint for change",
OL,8,Fthe report outlines practical measures
OL,9,Fto increase inclusion ` including more
OL,10,Fapprenticeships, fairer recruitment
OL,11,Fpractices, and dedicated funding to
OL,12,Fimprove access for underrepresented
OL,13,Fgroups.
OL,15,FWhile the report takes Greater
OL,16,FManchester as a pilot region for
OL,17,Fimplementation, Gilmore and Afzal say
OL,18,Fits findings are intended to inform a
OL,19,Fnational conversation on equality and
OL,20,Fopportunity within the creative sector.
